The Salwator City estate is a protected, fully secure complex, ideal for young married couples and working people who require efficient public transport. Thanks to the proximity of the public transport stop ("Zarzecze" - bus stop and "Wesele" - tram stop) you can reach the very center of the city in a few minutes, and the journey to the Old Town via a fast tram will take no more than 12 minutes. Parking spaces are available for residents in the enclosed area - entry behind the barrier. Nearby, there is a well-developed commercial and service infrastructure, which includes, among others: Biedronka supermarket, Pizza Factory pizzeria, Żabka, cosmetic points, gym, swimming pool, tennis court. The estate is a very good solution for people working in the center or studying at Krakow's universities, to which access is almost perfect.

FLAT
Apartment is located on the 2'nd floor and has an area of 32.33 sq m. It consists of:
- living room with kitchenette and balcony: kitchen furniture and household appliances in the building (induction hob, oven, dishwasher, hood, fridge-freezer), sofa, TV cabinet, coffee table, table with chairs;
- bedroom with balcony: bed with mattress, chest of drawers;
- fully equipped bathroom: shower cubicle, toilet, washing machine, sink with drawers, towel rail radiator;
- hall: wardrobe with mirrors, shoe cabinets.
The balcony of the apartment is in the form of a loggia and has an area of almost 4 sq m. The flat faces north and west.
Parking spaces are available for residents in the enclosed area.

